title: 83 Modern Marvels Episodes - The History Channel
description:
Various Modern Marvels episodes I&#039;ve collected over the years.  83 Episodes in all downloaded from various torrents and compiled here.  If you don&#039;t like the resolution, I&#039;m sorry - I can&#039;t do anything about it, I&#039;m just compiling these episodes here.  Also, I left them as individual files, so you can select which ones you want to download individually from the torrent.  Its a pain when you have to download a bunch of .rar files.  If some of you have episodes not listed here, I suggest you do the same and compile a torrent of your episodes.  I&#039;m trying to collect more, but it&#039;s getting harder and harder to find ones I don&#039;t already have.

Various resolutions and bitrates.  Credits to all the original uploaders - Thanks!
